        <p><span style="font-weight: 400">At The Untold Story, we start every project not with cameras but with questions:</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400"><span style="font-weight: 400">What does your brand stand for?</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400"><span style="font-weight: 400">Who are you truly talking to?</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400"><span style="font-weight: 400">What is the change you want to evoke in your audience?</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400">By answering these, we shape </span><b>strategic video narratives</b><span style="font-weight: 400"> that go beyond aesthetics.</span></p>		
